#

Chocolate Cinnamon Oatmeal Delight

15 min
$3.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy (if using milk)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastComfort FoodQuickHealthy

Description

A warm and comforting bowl of oatmeal infused with rich chocolate and a hint of cinnamon, perfect for a cozy breakfast.

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 1 cup
  • milk (or dairy-free alternative): 2 cups
  • cocoa powder: 2 tablespoons
  • brown sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • ground cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: a pinch
  • chocolate chips (optional): 2 tablespoons
  • fresh fruit (like bananas or berries): for topping
